Welcome on board the Alces Flight Launch service<%= launching_branding_header %>.

Your <%= @cluster_spec_name %> "<%= @cluster_name %>" will begin launching shortly.
<%- if @payment.has_expiration? -%>
Once you are in flight, the evaluation period for your Alces Flight Compute
HPC cluster will be <%= @runtime %>.  Please remember to save your work as you go
as, once the trial completes, the cluster will shutdown automatically.
<%- elsif @max_credit_usage.present? -%>
This cluster will consume your compute units until it is terminated or it
reaches its limit of <%= @max_credit_usage %> compute <%=
'unit'.pluralize(@max_credit_usage) %>.  Should your account run out of
compute units then your cluster will begin to shut down automatically.
During this time you will have access to your cluster's login node for <%=
@grace_period_in_hours %>  <%= 'hour'.pluralize(@grace_period_in_hours) %> to
enable you to save your work.  Please remember to save your work as you go.
<%- else -%>
This cluster will consume your compute units until it is terminated.  Should
your account run out of compute units then your cluster will begin to shut down
automatically.  During this time you will have access to your cluster's login
node for <%= @grace_period_in_hours %>  <%= 'hour'.pluralize(@grace_period_in_hours) %>
to enable you to save your work.  Please remember to save your work as you go.
<%- end -%>

You will receive another email shortly letting you know that your Alces Flight
Compute HPC cluster is available for use.

<% note do %>
  You are receiving this email because you have started an Alces Flight
  Compute HPC cluster with the Alces Flight Launch service.
<% end %>
<%= render 'shared/contact_us' %>
See you in the air soon!

The Alces Flight Crew.
